Performing CV using random forest, allowing multiple cores

rfCV_multi.Rd

Performing CV using random forest, allowing multiple cores

rfCV_multi(x, y, nFolds = 5, nExp, cores = 1, ntree = 500)

Arguments

x

design matrix
y

factor
nFolds

number of CV folds
nExp

number of loops
cores

number of cores to perform the CV
ntree

number of trees

Examples

x = iris[51:150, -5]
y = factor(iris[51:150, 5])
tmp2 = rfCV_multi(x = x, y = y,
                   nFolds = 5, nExp = 100, cores = 1, ntree = 100)
